Description: Event-driven security suite for Linux shared hosting
 Jabali Security provides real-time file monitoring, heuristic malware
 detection, YARA-X scanning, process monitoring, and automated threat
 response for shared hosting environments. Lightweight alternative to
 Imunify360 with under 100MB memory footprint.
